    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as expected with no mechanical issues to report. Inside, the upholstery is clean with only minor signs of use, and all electronic features, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, though you may find a few small stone chips on the hood consistent with regular driving. It serves as a reliable daily driver that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
