    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so sad to let this beauty go. It\u2019s been absolutely babied since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! There isn't a scratch or a smudge on it, and the interior is still looking pristine. If you\u2019ve been searching for a ride that\u2019s basically in perfect shape and ready for a new home, this is definitely the one. Come take a look\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-quality E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with its signature 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen utilizes a seven-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a GKN-sourced variable M differential for surgical power distribution. The chassis dynamics are managed via Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing a wide bandwidth between compliance and track-ready stiffness. Mechanically overhauled with preventative rod bearing replacement and fresh throttle actuators, the drivetrain is synchronized to factory tolerances. The exterior features original paint with no swirling or pitting, while the interior remains tensioned and free of bolster wear. A definitive collector-grade vehicle with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
