    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle in absolute showroom condition that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements and driven only on fair-weather days. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium upholstery is taut and unmarked, the dashboard is pristine, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and technological feature operates with factory-spec precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule with all records organized in a comprehensive binder. Included are the original window sticker, two sets of keys, and all factory manuals. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen for the buyer who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
